            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "the game is great i know ea gets hate on fc like it is not as good as the fifas but my last played played fifa was fifa 19 so coming from that to fc 25 feels like a great leap and i am liking it and i cant belive how overpowered the power shot is it makes any shot in the box a goal and also it is just great fun in career mode i always love to start career mode and pour my time on the player i am building to become and also there is champions league and many more tournaments which are great they are honestly great fun i always love to try seeing how far i can go with different teams in the ucl. And kick off is as always quick fun i dont play the  ultimate team because like to play and try to beat hard ai's or beat my friends in kick off but still seeing how rest of the game is nice and polished it is great i sometimes see some graphical mistakes like light and shirt physics but other than that fine but the commentry dialogues don't change much from old fifa but the music catalogues so much more bigger now overall a great game. Currently i played 4 hours but do plan on playing much more but this is my initial review."
